                <h2>WizWrite 1.1.0</h2>
                <p>New Local Transcripts feature and improved authentication!</p>
                <h3>New Features</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Local Transcripts:</strong> Upload audio files (MP3, WAV, M4A) for local-only transcription - nothing sent to cloud</li>
                    <li><strong>Update Reminders:</strong> Menu bar now shows when updates are available</li>
                </ul>
                <h3>Improvements</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Auth Hardening:</strong> Automatic logout on session expiration with clear messaging</li>
                    <li><strong>Session Validation:</strong> App validates login on launch</li>
                    <li><strong>Dynamic Version:</strong> Settings now shows version automatically</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
